# Performance Rules

## Frame Budget
- Target: 16ms per frame (60fps)
- Use const constructors everywhere possible
- Use ConsumerWidget for Riverpod, not ConsumerStatefulWidget unless lifecycle needed

## Rebuild Minimization
- Use ref.watch with select() for granular rebuilds
- Extract sub-widgets rather than large build() methods
- Use const for static subtrees

## Lists
- SliverList/SliverGrid for lists >20 items
- Use itemExtent when items have fixed height
- Never ListView without itemCount (unbounded)
- Never nest ScrollViews without NeverScrollableScrollPhysics

## Forbidden in build()
- Network calls
- File I/O
- Heavy computation
- setState cascades
- Provider creation
